ider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"QuantityInputComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tag inputs"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Quantity inputs","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","title":"OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"Theme Orange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUD